fields.name: Sirloin
fields.description: The popular Sirloin cut has a fine silky texture and rich marbling providing our sirloin steak a beautiful flavour and perfect tenderness.
fields.additional_information: Suitable for freezing, Weight: Approx 250-300g, Supplied raw.

fields.name: Fillet
fields.description: The Fillet is known for being tender, luxurious with elegant and subtle flavours. It is lean yet it will melt in your mouth with its compact shape.
fields.additional_information: Suitable for freezing, Weight: Approx 200-250g, Supplied raw.

fields.name: Rib Eye
fields.description: The Rib Eye steak is popular for its rich marbling and natural core of fat which runs through the meat, making it tender and juicy.
fields.additional_information: Suitable for freezing, Weight: Approx 230-280g, Supplied raw.

fields.name: Rump
fields.description: The Rump steak is marbled with fat on the outer layer, making it exceptionally flavourful.
fields.additional_information: Suitable for freezing, Weight: Approx 230-280g, Supplied raw.

fields.name: T-Bone
fields.description: The prime T-Bone steak is cut through and left on the bone to include both sirloin and fillet with maximum tenderness and flavour. This is one of the premium steaks and requires skill to prepare correctly.
fields.additional_information: Suitable for freezing, Weight: Approx 450-500g, Supplied raw.

fields.name: Tomahawk
fields.description: The Tomahawk cut is the king of steaks due to its large, tomahawk axe like appearance. With the bone separating two large juicy sections of meat, the Tomahawk is enough to feed multiple meat lovers.
fields.additional_information: Suitable for freezing, Weight: Approx 900g-1100g, Supplied raw.

fields.name: Chicken Wings
fields.description: Everyone loves our chicken wings! They have become our customers prime choice as they can be cooked in a variety of ways from fried to grilled and marinated in different sauces & spices.
fields.additional_information: Suitable for freezing, Weight: Price per KG, Supplied raw.

fields.name: Chicken Legs
fields.description: Not as popular as the chicken wings, but the chicken legs are also a staple among our customers. They can also be cooked and marinated in different ways to perfection for you and your family & friends to enjoy!
fields.additional_information: Suitable for freezing, Weight: Price per KG, Supplied raw.

fields.name: Chicken Breast(Boneless)
fields.description: The chicken breast is the most special cut that most people want to purchase as it is filled with protein and low fat content. Aside from the nutritional benefits, chicken breasts are flavourful and have a capacity to absorb a variety of ingredients, Plus its boneless, so less hassle for the kids!
fields.additional_information: Suitable for freezing, Weight: Price per KG, Supplied raw.

fields.name: Whole Chicken
fields.description: The whole chicken is definitely for those who want to share their chicken with others. The option to have a chicken leg, chicken wings or even chicken breast all in one is a huge benefit to all. Unless, youre a bodybuilder who has high protein consumption of course!
fields.additional_information: Suitable for freezing, Weight: Price per KG, Supplied raw.

fields.name: Sheep Mix
fields.description: Our sheep meat is derived from a domestic sheep aged 1 to 2 years of age. Having a distinctive taste and quality tenderness, it can be cooked to perfection in many different ways.
fields.additional_information: Suitable for freezing, Weight: Price per Box, Supplied raw.

fields.name: Lamb Chop
fields.description: Lamb chops are a staple in many different cuisines. They are scrumptious, tender and can be prepared in a variety of ways. Lamb chops possess a uniquely rich character that pairs well with different herbs & spices.
fields.additional_information: Suitable for freezing, Weight: Price per KG, Supplied raw.

fields.name: Leg of Lamb
fields.description: The leg of lamb is a British favourite with an abundance of lean and succulent meat ideal for a perfect Sunday roast with your family.
fields.additional_information: Suitable for freezing, Weight: Approx 2.6 to 3.0kg, Supplied raw.

fields.name: Sushi Platter (New In)
fields.description: Introducing our new product - the Sushi Platter. Yes, The Halal Butcher is now providing customers with sushi boxes to take home or on the go! More sushi platters will come in the future.
fields.additional_information: Supplied in a box. Contents include: Salmon Nigiri, Crab & Cucumber Chumaki, Fried Prawn Chumaki, Spicy Salmon Roll with Soy Sauce & Wasabi.

fields.name: Beef Burger Patties
fields.description: These beef burger patties are perfect for BBQ's and assembling quick burgers for lunch/dinner as the meat is already compressed. Ready to be marinated in your choice of herbs & spices and cooked to perfection.
fields.additional_information: Suitable for freezing, Supplied in packs of 6.
